01:16:36.719 --> 01:16:38.870
persecution and

01:16:39.640 --> 01:16:44.590
that racial

01:16:44.600 --> 01:16:48.790
trash, the racial trash, man, the racial

01:16:48.800 --> 01:16:53.669
hurt, Alabama, these areas, it's still

01:16:53.679 --> 01:16:56.950
