01:19:10.159 --> 01:19:13.709
Back pay—that's what I'm hearing Him say: back

01:19:13.709 --> 01:19:13.719
pay,

01:19:13.719 --> 01:19:18.229
back

01:19:18.229 --> 01:19:18.239
pay.

01:19:18.239 --> 01:19:20.630
